# Documentation Structure

## Categories
- setup: Project setup and configuration guides
- components: Documentation for reusable components
- styles: Tailwind usage guidelines and custom styles
- testing: Testing strategies and patterns
- deployment: Deployment procedures

## File Organization
- Use descriptive filenames in kebab-case
- Group related documentation in subdirectories
- Include code examples where applicable
- Keep documentation updated with code changes

## Cross-Referencing
- Use @ tags to reference specific files
- Link to official documentation for external libraries
- Include version information for all dependencies
- Use consistent terminology throughout docs